               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="186601290047"></xptr>
               <p>—on the afternoon of 14th January, about a quarter to 4, I was in my shop, and saw the prisoner take a coat off my rail inside the shop—he ran away and I ran after him, but could not catch him—I did not lose sight of him—this is it (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>).</p>
               <p>
